    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "On 6-3-54 an ad appeared in the \"Cincinnati Enquirer,\" a newspaper of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "general circulation, Cincinnati, Ohio, to the effect that on 6-11-54 a",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "program would be presented at Taft Auditorium, Cincinnati, Ohio, on \"The",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "Real Flying Saucer Story.\" The advertisement which Mr. [REDACTED] exhibited",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "disclosed no sponsor for this program and it was only noted on the ad",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "that tickets for the program sold for $2.00 per person and would be on sale",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "at the Central Ticket Office in Cincinnati.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "Mr. [REDACTED] advised that although he belongs to no organization",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "interested in flying saucers, he has been interested in this subject and",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "has been interested to the extent that he desired to know the sponsorship",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "of the program. He stated that he found out from the Central Ticket Office",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "that the ad had been placed by [REDACTED]",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "Ferndale 20, Michigan. He advised that he telephonically contacted [REDACTED]",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "on 6-3-54 and [REDACTED] stated that he was only the agent for renting the",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "hall and that he was acting on behalf of [REDACTED] and [REDACTED]",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "[REDACTED] He stated that on 6-4-54 [REDACTED] called him back and told",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "him that there had been a disagreement between [REDACTED] and",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "[REDACTED] over [REDACTED] arrangements for the sale of tickets for the",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "program and the renting of the hall.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "[REDACTED] advised that at this time [REDACTED] said nothing to discredit",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
